General.Name: Max Stock Ltd
General.Description: Max Stock Ltd. operates various discount stores in Israel. Its stores provide products in various categories, including school supplies, disposable dishes, clothing and textiles, arts and crafts, furniture, home accessories and gifts, toys, cleaning products, plasticware, kitchen and cooking utensils, bithdays, and tools and hardware. The company is based in Caesarea, Israel.
